            <br /><br />
            The rise of tools like <strong>Make.com</strong> (formerly Integromat), <strong>Systeme.io</strong>, and connected Google Sheets has fundamentally changed what's achievable on a $0 software budget. Common tasks now automatable for free include: order processing, inventory sync, customer segmentation, email triggers, review requests, reporting pipelines, and cross-platform data sync.
